{
  "texts": [
    "Information extraction was tested on six models: Med42-70b, Mixtral-8x7B-Instruct-v0.1, Llama-3-70b, Flan-T5-XXL, Flan-UL2, and GPT-4.",
    "The chunk embedding model was BAAI Generalized Embeddings Large English v1.5, and for model distillation, we fine-tuned Bio+ClinicalBERT (Supplementary Table 22).",
    "Model usage parameters for NER and information extraction are reported in Supplementary Table 23.",
    "a Fine-tuned BERT F1 score higher than the trainer model's F1 score on the same held-out test set.",
    "npj Digital Medicine | (2025) 8:45"
  ]
